            <div class="clearfix text-formatted field field--name-field-body field--type-text-long field--label-hidden field__item"><p>Lansdowne Park is a world-class attraction that blends modern amenities, courtyards, heritage buildings and green space. Located in the heart of the city, this urban destination hosts events, community programming and recreation activities year-round.&nbsp;</p>
